(operational_tier is the safer business-control layer.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| Tier | Recommended action | Business assumption |) Tj
T*
(|---|---|---|) Tj
T*
(| suppress | Exclude from billing or downstream metrics after policy approval. | The) Tj
T*
(organisation accepts limited review risk for high-confidence traffic. |) Tj
T*
(| quarantine | Hold, delay, sample, or manually review before suppression. | Ambiguous) Tj
T*
(traffic should not be automatically removed. |) Tj
T*
(| monitor | Keep for trend monitoring and future labels. | Non-selected traffic can) Tj
T*
(still help detect drift later. |) Tj
