(text) Tj
T*
(combined_score > 0.568053) Tj
T*
(or heuristic_score >= 0.62) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The combined-score threshold is the run-specific 97.5th-percentile cutoff. It) Tj
T*
(keeps the selected volume stable for an unlabelled dataset while letting the ML) Tj
T*
(model influence borderline cases.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The heuristic override protects high-confidence, explainable rule hits. For) Tj
T*
(example, a strongly repeated query/domain pattern with mechanical timing should) Tj
T*
(not be missed only because the anomaly ranking moved after a feature change.) Tj
T*
() Tj
